    (1, 'ACTION', 'Covers attacking with Melee and Ranged Weapons, Dashing and any other activity where the player must roll on the Action Success Chart to make an Action. This roll can be modified by the opposing player by using BLOOD MARKERS. Each marker causes -1 DICE penalty to the roll.'),
